title: The most important interpretation of 20 seeing a dog in a dream by Ibn Sirin

preview.html: Seeing a dog in a dream is one of the most common dreams that we always have, which causes us anxiety. This vision has many interpretations that interpreters have encountered as indicating a weak enemy or a corrupt person. It can express a stingy man, as Sheikh Al-Nabulsi said, and we will learn about all the interpretations of this vision through this article.The dog in a dreamThe dog in a dreamImam Al-Nabulsi says: A dog in a dream is evidence of an evil and silly person, but if it is savage, then it is a person of knowledge and does not work. It does not benefit himself or others. A white dog in a dream is a reference to a cheerful boy who has grown from what is forbidden and illegal, and a gray dog ​​is a reference to a hypocritical and foolish person who lacks wisdom in his actions. Dreaming of a dog in a dream is evidence of a cold enemy who will not harm him at all if he does not It causes harm to the fortuneteller, but a mad dog means a reckless enemy or a shameless thief. A dog’s saliva in a dream is a symbol of the poisonous words that the dreamer hears from his enemy and causes him great sadness. A dog in a dream by Ibn Sirin Ibn Sirin says that a dog barking in a dream is evidence that the dreamer is afflicted with a disease. And fever, but if you see that dogs are chasing you, this means that you are with bad friends and you must stay away from them. To dream of a dog in a dream means a tyrannical person who does not take the opinion of anyone around him and causes problems for his life partner. As for the man feeding the dog, it is evidence that the anxiety has ended. And it increased. In livelihood.Leaning on a dog in a dream is a sign that you will soon get rid of enemies. As for seeing dogs barking at you, it means that your partner is cheating on you, and the vision also symbolizes separation and divorce. The dog in a dream according to Al-Nabulsi. Al-Nabulsi interpreted seeing a dog in a dream as evidence that the dreamer has many bad qualities, but he does not seek to correct them. Seeing a female dog in bed In a dream, it is a bad vision and warns that you are in a relationship with a cheerful woman and you should stay away from her because she will cause you a lot of problems. Seeing dogs in a dream by Ibn Shaheen Ibn Shaheen says that seeing red dogs in a dream is evidence of negative events and falling into sin and transgression, and as for eating dog meat, it is Victory over enemies and profit from them. Buying a dog in a dream from a merchant is evidence of losing money, but he will make up for it soon. Small dogs in a dream are a sign of good and opinionated children, but if there is a black puppy among them, this means bad morals in children. The dog in A dream for a single woman: A dog in one dream is not good, it is a sign of someone making you sick, and if it is black then it means a bad young man who does not trust you and wants to harm you. In chaos and committing sins. A white dog in a dream that he is single is a sign of a friend of yours who shows you a good way and is in reality your enemy. Being attacked by dogs means serious problems and fears will find you. As for a dog bite, it means harm, but from a weak and cowardly person. Escaping from dogs in an unmarried woman’s dream is a sign of liberation from all the evil that surrounds her. What is T

title: Learn about the interpretation of fish in a dream according to Ibn Sirin and leading scholars

preview.html: Dreaming of fish in a dream has always been associated with goodness, as it is one of the symbols that indicate abundance in living and abundance of money in most interpretations, but it can be a sign of loss and not benefiting or obtaining money but through a forbidden path. The interpretation varies according to the condition and color of the fish and we will discuss all the indicators for seeing it. Fish in a dream through this article.Fish in a dreamFish in a dreamFish in a dream, if the number is many and the dreamer cannot own much, then this means a lot of money in a legal way that the dreamer will earn, but if the number is limited to less than four, then this means that number One of the wives in his life is a fortune teller. As for eating a large fish, which is characterized by its soft texture, this means that it is very good, but if it is small and dry, then it is an act of no good, or an increase in debts and burdens without benefit. In their decision. Seeing grilled fish in a dream means abundant goodness for the dreamer, and Ibn Shaheen says that it is an expression of satisfying a need, an answer to prayer, and freedom from problems and troubles. Al-Nabulsi says: If the fish is soft or without scales: this is evidence of it earning money by deceiving people and deceiving each other or An act of falsehood. A dream about eating fish without thorns symbolizes an easy life in which the dreamer does not get tired. As for fish with thorns, it means little sustenance after many problems and difficulties. Fish in a dream by Ibn Sirin. Ibn Sirin says about the interpretation of a dream about a fish that it is a sign of abundance in life. The near future, and it may be money or livelihood for a good wife and many offspring, marriage to a single relative, or a lady’s pregnancy. Dreaming of a dead fish in a man’s dream is a sign of many difficulties and crises, and eating it means health problems and failure to achieve goals. Ibn Sirin says about fish. Colorful neighborhood, it is a marriage to a beautiful girl with one personality, but if he catches her, this is evidence of achieving goals without many problems in life. Eating fish in a dream is evidence that the dreamer is an ambitious person who insists on achieving goals if its taste is sweet, but if its taste is Bitter means that he obtains money from forbidden sources. What is the interpretation of seeing fish in a dream for Imam Al-Sadiq? In many of his interpretations, Imam Al-Sadiq sees that a fish in a dream is undesirable and expresses exposure to serious injustice, especially if its jaws are open and large in size. Collection of fish Clothes are evidence of the dreamer’s intelligence in the world and his tireless efforts to collect money, but if he obtained it while sitting in the sea without effort, this means a serious problem, contrary to what many interpreters interpret. Fish in a dream for a single woman. Ibn Sirin says that seeing fish for single women is evidence of... A positive transformation in life, satisfaction of desires and the ability to achieve goals, if they are lively and energetic. An unmarried girl’s dream of raw fish is an unfavorable vision and indicates that you are going through a period of great troubles, accompanied by vacancy with sadness, but most likely it is a short period and will pass quickly.
